    Leverage FastTrack and Partner Services to support Microsoft 365 - Use FastTrack to help with your Microsoft 365 deployment

    »

    1. As the Enterprise Administrator for Fabrikam, you’re planning the company’s migration to Microsoft 365. To help you with this process, you’re considering using Microsoft’s FastTrack service. You know that with FastTrack, Microsoft will provide Fabrikam with personalized assistance. However, you’re not sure how long the service will be available. How long is FastTrack available to a customer?

      FastTrack provides personalized assistance as long as the customer’s subscription is active

      FastTrack provides personalized assistance until the customer’s Microsoft 365 tenant has been deployed

      FastTrack provides personalized assistance for up to one year after the customer has purchased its Microsoft 365 subscription
